<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Map 7. Known distribution of Oriental species of genus Dasiosoma: ● Dasiosoma hirsutum (Bates) ★ Dasiosoma maindroni (Tian & Deuve) ▲ Dasiosoma quadraticolle sp. n. ◆ Dasiosoma bellum (Habu) ■ Dasiosoma indicum (Kirschenhofer)." , "Figure 88. Median lobe of male genitalia, right-lateral, ventral, left-lateral, dorsal views of Dasiosoma indicum (Kirschenhofer), holotype." , "Figures 55 - 60. Type materials, scale bars = 2.0 mm: 55 Holotype of Dasiosoma sudanicum Basilewsky 56 Holotype of Dasiosoma ivorense Basilewsky 57 Holotype of Diamella indica Kirschenhofer [= Dasiosoma indicum (Kirschenhofer)] 58 Paratype of Lachnoderma maindroni Tian & Deuve [= Dasiosoma maindroni (Tian & Deuve)] 59 Lectotype of Singlis hirsutus Bates [= Dasiosoma hirsutum (Bates)] 60 The \" lectotype \" designated by Tian & Deuve, 2001 for Singlis hirsutus Bates." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/29729" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/29706" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/29683" .

